A stripped down Windows Driver Kit (WDK) v7.1.0 (aka 7600.16385.1).

Initial zip revision (x86.win.ddk.7600.16385.1.zip).

The following has been removed to reduce the size a little:
    bin\**\ia64\
    Catalog\
    Debug\
    help\
    lib\**\ia64\
    redist\
    src\
    tools\

Note! Other bits might have been omitted by the installer, as I attempted to 
      disable things we don't need (yet).

